WEBVTT

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:06.040
(Previously)
I really like you.

00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:07.960
Would you like to try dating me?

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:10.640
Please help me get back with your brother.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.079
I know.

00:00:13.080 --> 00:00:15.960
The one who brought me home was you…

00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:17.639
Please give me one more chance.

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:19.239
Time's up, Jimmy.

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:21.800
A guy like me never begs.

00:00:22.040 --> 00:00:26.279
That dentist customer already
asked P'Toh to be his boyfriend.

00:00:26.280 --> 00:00:28.440
Do you still want to be with me?

00:00:28.880 --> 00:00:29.880
Of course I do.

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:30.920
My answer is "yes."

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:05.800
"Love Alert"
(Episode 9)

00:03:06.280 --> 00:03:08.480
Toh, you should try this.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:19.400
How is it? Good?

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:21.800
Yes, it's good.

00:03:22.600 --> 00:03:25.160
See? I told you to trust my taste.

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:28.960
Next time, I'll take you
to more great places.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:44.960
Try this one too.

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:48.800
Toh?

00:03:50.280 --> 00:03:51.280
Toh...

00:03:51.640 --> 00:03:52.640
Yes?

00:03:53.600 --> 00:03:54.960
Is something wrong?

00:03:56.600 --> 00:03:57.760
Nothing's wrong.

00:03:58.920 --> 00:03:59.920
Let's just keep eating.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:45.520
Why does it have to hurt this much?

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.040
So, Toh.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:40.600
Where do you see yourself
in the next two years?

00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:43.200
Nothing big, really.

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:49.840
I just want to grow the café and take care
of Teh until he can stand on his own feet.

00:05:52.240 --> 00:05:55.840
So, your life is only about the cafe
and your brother right now?

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:03.800
P'Freeze, please don't take it that way.

00:06:04.880 --> 00:06:07.640
I was talking about my life as of right
now.

00:06:09.200 --> 00:06:13.560
As for us, I'd like to take things
slow and get to know each other better.

00:06:14.880 --> 00:06:17.160
I get it.

00:06:22.440 --> 00:06:26.320
But... why the sudden question?

00:06:26.920 --> 00:06:29.400
I felt like I was in a job interview.

00:06:32.520 --> 00:06:35.560
Well, in two years, I have
to study abroad in England.

00:06:38.640 --> 00:06:41.599
I just wanted to know what your plans are.

00:06:41.600 --> 00:06:47.400
And... is there any possibility that...
you'd move there with me?

00:06:56.760 --> 00:06:59.920
Hey... if you don't have
an answer yet, that's totally fine.

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:03.320
I know how much you
care about the café and Teh.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:07.600
Let's wait until the time comes.

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:13.040
Please don't be mad at me.

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:16.520
I'm not mad.

00:07:17.800 --> 00:07:19.160
I'm just...

00:07:19.880 --> 00:07:21.360
a little surprised.

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:24.240
I didn't expect things to move this fast.

00:07:26.680 --> 00:07:28.040
Like I said,

00:07:29.520 --> 00:07:36.920
I still want to take my time with you.
I don't want to rush into anything.

00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:40.960
I understand.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:49.160
I'm terrible, aren't I? We've only been together
for a day and I'm already being so impatient.

00:08:23.960 --> 00:08:25.560
I would never hurt you.

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:29.800
You're too precious...

00:08:31.760 --> 00:08:33.360
And yet...

00:08:39.320 --> 00:08:41.400
so tempting to break.

00:08:44.440 --> 00:08:47.080
I messed up.

00:08:48.440 --> 00:08:49.559
Please give me one more chance.

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:51.280
Time's up, Jimmy.

00:08:52.240 --> 00:08:54.480
I love you, P'Toh!

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:59.839
He told us he ended it
because he was bored.

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:04.640
A guy like me never begs. And I've
never fallen in love with anyone either.

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:14.600
Did you ever really love me?

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:21.240
What is going on in your mind, Jimmy?

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:26.600
I don't have any water.

00:10:27.080 --> 00:10:28.080
Want a beer?

00:10:37.920 --> 00:10:40.920
Jim... you really love him that much?

00:10:47.400 --> 00:10:49.240
I didn't thought so either…

00:10:52.680 --> 00:10:54.960
that I'd love P'Toh this much.

00:11:00.640 --> 00:11:01.680
Run...

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:11.560
I'm so sorry.

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:19.920
For everything I did to hurt you.

00:11:22.760 --> 00:11:24.160
I was a total jerk.

00:11:34.760 --> 00:11:38.400
It's okay. That's all in the past now.

00:11:49.760 --> 00:11:56.440
No matter what, Jimmy...
you were the best love I ever had.

00:12:07.400 --> 00:12:09.440
Can we be together again?

00:12:21.040 --> 00:12:23.680
I can't love anyone else anymore, Run.

00:12:31.080 --> 00:12:33.360
It's only P'Toh.

00:12:46.800 --> 00:12:49.800
But he doesn't love me anymore.

00:13:03.880 --> 00:13:06.000
I miss him so much.

00:13:15.120 --> 00:13:16.720
What am I supposed to do?

00:13:36.520 --> 00:13:38.720
I'm such an asshole.

00:13:51.765 --> 00:13:56.320
P'Toh, I heard you're dating
Dr. Freeze. I'm so happy for you.

00:13:59.560 --> 00:14:01.200
P'Toh…

00:14:01.720 --> 00:14:04.160
are you sure it's what your heart wants?

00:14:08.520 --> 00:14:11.720
Teh, I told you to stay back and let him
be.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:15.960
I want to give P'Freeze a chance.

00:14:16.600 --> 00:14:21.040
And more importantly,
I want to give myself a chance too.

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:23.400
That's good then.

00:14:25.360 --> 00:14:27.680
I just want you to be happy.

00:14:35.200 --> 00:14:36.320
Toh!

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:38.200
I'm here.

00:14:42.720 --> 00:14:44.000
See you guys later.

00:14:55.880 --> 00:14:58.320
Wanna check on your best friend?

00:15:00.520 --> 00:15:01.960
I'll leave him be.

00:15:02.880 --> 00:15:05.920
Some scars just need to heal on their own.

00:18:14.440 --> 00:18:15.600
Fah!

00:18:18.400 --> 00:18:20.520
I'm done with my exams!

00:18:30.760 --> 00:18:32.360
How was it?

00:18:35.040 --> 00:18:38.680
At least… I didn't leave the paper blank.

00:18:40.560 --> 00:18:46.040
So, no expectations, no disappointments.

00:18:48.640 --> 00:18:49.880
Let's have a vacation.

00:18:51.680 --> 00:18:53.080
Can we go to Taiwan?

00:18:54.840 --> 00:18:58.320
Sure. I've been wanting
to go there for a photoshoot.

00:18:59.200 --> 00:19:00.920
You're the sweetest.

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:37.600
Jimmy,

00:19:40.560 --> 00:19:44.520
Are you still drinking during finals week?

00:19:45.480 --> 00:19:47.360
I ran out of water at home.

00:19:50.040 --> 00:19:52.000
Are you back with Run?

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:53.600
No... I'm not.

00:20:15.680 --> 00:20:19.800
I just checked on Jim.
He looks like total crap.

00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:25.880
But he insisted that
he's not back with Run.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:30.280
Are you sure he's not lying?

00:20:32.040 --> 00:20:34.520
You're being way too hard on him.

00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:38.320
I can't help it. Your
friend hasn't been nice.

00:20:38.960 --> 00:20:42.240
And besides, you're always taking his side.

00:20:44.840 --> 00:20:48.840
I'll only believe it when I
hear it from his ex's mouth.

00:20:53.720 --> 00:20:56.800
P'Fah. Teh.

00:21:10.520 --> 00:21:16.560
So, that's everything. I tried to get back
with him, but he wouldn't give me a chance.

00:21:17.760 --> 00:21:23.440
And you came to us because you
want our help to get back with Jimmy?

00:21:24.400 --> 00:21:31.000
No. I just want Jim to be himself again.
He truly, deeply loves P'Toh.

00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:54.440
Toh,

00:21:57.200 --> 00:22:01.800
take a break. I bought you some porridge.
Eat it before taking your meds.

00:22:03.040 --> 00:22:04.680
Thank you, P'Freeze.

00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:09.000
You shouldn't have gone to the trouble.

00:22:10.000 --> 00:22:13.800
Don't mention it. I also got you
some vitamins and medicines.

00:22:14.200 --> 00:22:19.400
I noticed your cabinet
was missing some of these.

00:22:22.520 --> 00:22:25.120
Yes, P'Freeze. Thank you so much.

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:34.759
And about these household supplies...
the ones you're using aren't great.

00:22:34.760 --> 00:22:40.360
I bought better ones to replace them. They're
more expensive but much higher quality.

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:46.680
If you need anything,
don't hesitate to tell me.

00:22:48.280 --> 00:22:53.840
Eat up, Toh. I'll go put these
away at your house for you.

00:23:29.040 --> 00:23:34.120
Teh told me he'd prepare my meds,
but why did he leave them here?

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:41.080
Serves Jimmy right.
He had a gem but couldn't keep it.

00:24:41.600 --> 00:24:46.160
Now, P'Toh is so happy with Dr. Freeze.

00:24:47.240 --> 00:24:48.400
Happy?

00:24:49.520 --> 00:24:51.200
I don't think so.

00:24:51.960 --> 00:24:54.720
I can feel he's not happy.

00:24:56.160 --> 00:25:00.600
He was forcing that smile.
It's nothing like when he was with Jim.

00:25:00.920 --> 00:25:03.520
Are you taking his side again?

00:25:04.160 --> 00:25:06.760
Can't you remember what he did to P'Toh?

00:25:07.400 --> 00:25:12.840
I remember. But I believe everyone
deserves a second chance.

00:25:13.800 --> 00:25:19.400
Not just Jim, but P'Toh deserves
to give his own heart a chance too.

00:25:20.960 --> 00:25:22.080
How did you become so wise?

00:25:24.800 --> 00:25:26.840
It's because I'm in love.

00:25:29.320 --> 00:25:33.680
And besides, he's my own flesh and blood.

00:25:34.800 --> 00:25:37.600
How could I not know
how my own brother feels?

00:25:39.120 --> 00:25:40.120
What?

00:25:44.240 --> 00:25:45.400
A hug?

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:48.000
What's gotten into you?

00:25:51.160 --> 00:25:52.400
Please?

00:25:53.360 --> 00:25:55.240
Encouragement.

00:25:57.480 --> 00:25:58.880
Encouragement.

00:26:23.720 --> 00:26:24.880
What are you doing?

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:32.800
Give me some love.

00:26:37.640 --> 00:26:38.800
You pervert.

00:26:40.680 --> 00:26:42.120
Want me to stop?

00:29:07.800 --> 00:29:08.840
I know…

00:29:10.240 --> 00:29:12.080
I should love myself more.

00:29:15.920 --> 00:29:19.280
But the person I love
doesn't love me anymore.

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:24.480
If I'm not drunk...

00:29:26.800 --> 00:29:28.960
I can't stop missing your mom.

00:30:20.560 --> 00:30:23.160
I think this cream is better for you.

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:27.480
It's for sensitive skin.

00:30:33.440 --> 00:30:37.320
I noticed you've been having trouble
sleeping, so I got you this pillow spray.

00:30:37.600 --> 00:30:40.120
Lavender aroma. It helps you with sleeping.

00:30:40.800 --> 00:30:42.720
It's a natural essential oil.

00:30:43.320 --> 00:30:44.640
Sleep well.

00:31:22.280 --> 00:31:26.240
And don't forget your meds, my champion.

00:31:31.920 --> 00:31:32.920
Oh,

00:31:34.680 --> 00:31:36.240
whose is this?

00:31:48.760 --> 00:31:52.240
Aren't you supposed to be happy… Toh?

00:32:25.320 --> 00:32:27.520
You're early, P'Freeze.

00:32:43.720 --> 00:32:45.080
Here's your coffee.

00:32:45.160 --> 00:32:46.360
Thank you.

00:32:47.440 --> 00:32:49.080
Thanks for stopping by.

00:32:51.040 --> 00:32:52.480
Actually…

00:32:53.560 --> 00:32:55.640
I have something to talk to you about.

00:32:57.080 --> 00:32:58.320
What is it?

00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:00.880
It's about Jimmy.

00:33:11.040 --> 00:33:14.880
He's in a really bad shape.

00:34:51.080 --> 00:34:54.840
He pretends like he's
okay in front of others,

00:34:56.240 --> 00:35:00.240
but inside, he's completely shattered.

00:35:20.400 --> 00:35:23.480
I've never seen him this broken before.

00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:33.000
Why are you telling me this?

00:35:35.080 --> 00:35:37.720
My relationship with him… is over.

00:35:39.920 --> 00:35:41.440
There's no…

00:35:43.120 --> 00:35:45.200
going back for us.

00:35:47.720 --> 00:35:50.440
Not even as friends.

00:36:08.800 --> 00:36:14.320
Isn't this what you wanted?
Now you can get back together with him.

00:36:17.720 --> 00:36:21.400
It takes two to tango.

00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:29.600
I tried, but he won't let me in.

00:36:33.000 --> 00:36:35.000
His heart belongs only to you.

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:41.520
That day at his house...

00:36:42.600 --> 00:36:46.640
it was just concern between friends.

00:36:49.400 --> 00:36:54.840
I could never come between you two.

00:36:59.440 --> 00:37:01.120
Never.

00:37:10.520 --> 00:37:12.840
But... I have a boyfriend now.

00:37:14.560 --> 00:37:15.800
I know.

00:37:16.800 --> 00:37:18.800
But I'm telling you this…

00:37:20.440 --> 00:37:26.720
because I thought you might
have a way to make him feel better.

00:37:28.320 --> 00:37:30.360
At least...

00:37:32.320 --> 00:37:34.320
you two loved each other.

00:38:08.520 --> 00:38:10.320
Saensee, my boy.

00:38:25.080 --> 00:38:27.160
Let Daddy find you something to eat.

00:38:53.360 --> 00:38:54.680
Are you hungry?

00:39:01.000 --> 00:39:02.840
Meow, meow, meow…

00:39:12.320 --> 00:39:13.560
Want some treats?

00:39:20.400 --> 00:39:21.800
Meow, meow, meow…

00:39:59.200 --> 00:40:00.880
It's all my fault.

00:40:03.240 --> 00:40:05.280
I didn't take good care of him.

00:40:11.680 --> 00:40:13.600
I love you, P'Toh.

00:40:21.880 --> 00:40:23.680
Please come back to me.

00:40:48.480 --> 00:40:49.640
Excuse me!

00:40:55.400 --> 00:41:00.640
If it's not too much to ask,
could you tell me more about Toh's ex?

00:41:08.320 --> 00:41:10.520
Did Run really go talk to P'Toh for me?

00:41:11.280 --> 00:41:12.280
Yeah.

00:41:13.000 --> 00:41:16.560
He talked to me and
Fah before heading there.

00:41:17.400 --> 00:41:21.160
I thought you asked him to do it,

00:41:23.400 --> 00:41:26.600
but looking at your face now,
I know I was wrong.

00:41:28.800 --> 00:41:30.800
I truly love your brother.

00:41:31.800 --> 00:41:34.080
But he has someone new now.

00:41:36.400 --> 00:41:38.040
I don't want to cause any more trouble...

00:41:39.160 --> 00:41:40.160
for anyone.

00:41:42.440 --> 00:41:45.800
The only thing I can do is… accept it.

00:41:51.880 --> 00:41:53.920
You've really changed, Jimmy.

00:41:54.840 --> 00:41:56.400
Acting like a decent human being.

00:41:57.680 --> 00:42:02.560
If you'd acted like this from the start,
you'd probably be happy with him by now

00:42:03.160 --> 00:42:05.000
instead of moping around like a lost puppy.

00:42:07.920 --> 00:42:09.000
It's too late.

00:42:10.720 --> 00:42:12.360
No matter how much I improve...

00:42:14.640 --> 00:42:17.120
I can't compete with his new guy.

00:42:20.120 --> 00:42:21.120
I'm nothing…

00:42:23.520 --> 00:42:25.480
compared to him.

00:42:45.840 --> 00:42:46.840
Toh.

00:42:49.040 --> 00:42:50.040
P'Freeze.

00:42:52.760 --> 00:42:54.320
You bought so many things.

00:42:54.920 --> 00:42:59.000
Picanha and some red wine.
I'm making you steak tonight.

00:43:00.640 --> 00:43:02.080
What's the occasion?

00:43:02.720 --> 00:43:05.040
It's our two-month anniversary.

00:43:07.600 --> 00:43:10.520
I'll… make you a steak in your house.

00:43:11.680 --> 00:43:12.680
Okay.

00:43:38.560 --> 00:43:42.800
Aren't you going to fight for him?
Are you giving up that easily?

00:43:44.080 --> 00:43:45.640
What do I even have to fight him with?

00:43:46.440 --> 00:43:52.280
Your sincerity, determination,
"never give up" attitude, anything.

00:43:53.640 --> 00:43:57.320
Have you tried talking to him how you feel?

00:43:58.400 --> 00:44:00.920
Even Run went out of his
way to speak up for you.

00:44:04.600 --> 00:44:06.120
I'm going to see P'Toh.

00:44:06.880 --> 00:44:08.760
I'll ask for one last chance.

00:44:24.360 --> 00:44:25.760
Here, Toh.

00:44:26.960 --> 00:44:27.960
Take this.

00:44:29.120 --> 00:44:30.280
Thank you.

00:44:42.920 --> 00:44:44.080
So,

00:44:44.880 --> 00:44:46.320
how's my cooking?

00:44:49.720 --> 00:44:50.880
It's good.

00:44:54.360 --> 00:44:55.360
Toh,

00:44:57.040 --> 00:44:58.920
I have something to tell you.

00:45:02.280 --> 00:45:03.960
What is it?

00:45:05.040 --> 00:45:07.160
I got the scholarship to study in England.

00:45:16.720 --> 00:45:18.320
Come with me, Toh.

00:45:34.160 --> 00:45:36.240
Hey, Jimmy. I'll drive you home.

00:45:36.600 --> 00:45:38.560
It's okay. I want to be alone.

00:45:38.840 --> 00:45:39.960
Jimmy…

00:45:58.120 --> 00:46:03.000
But... I thought you said it
would be in another two years.

00:46:03.720 --> 00:46:06.360
Why is it so sudden?

00:46:06.880 --> 00:46:10.080
Well, the scholarship results just came in.

00:46:10.960 --> 00:46:14.400
I'll have to return as
a professor afterward.

00:46:15.680 --> 00:46:22.320
I was hesitant at first,
but a teaching career is very stable.

00:46:27.240 --> 00:46:28.240
But...

00:46:29.360 --> 00:46:31.800
I don't think I'm ready.

00:46:33.760 --> 00:46:37.720
I understand. It probably feels
like everything is moving too fast.

00:46:39.080 --> 00:46:42.320
We can learn more about
each other over there.

00:46:43.120 --> 00:46:48.800
It'll be just the two of us;
our relationship will be even stronger.

00:46:50.960 --> 00:46:55.360
And I'm not asking you to go
because I'm jealous or possessive.

00:46:56.640 --> 00:46:58.120
I trust you.

00:46:58.840 --> 00:47:02.400
I'm just afraid I won't be
able to stand missing you.

00:47:05.800 --> 00:47:07.400
Come with me.

00:47:21.600 --> 00:47:22.960
P'Freeze…

00:47:25.640 --> 00:47:27.080
let's break up.

00:47:34.040 --> 00:47:35.480
Why, Toh?

00:47:36.520 --> 00:47:40.960
Did I say something wrong?
Did I do something to hurt you?

00:47:42.840 --> 00:47:44.480
Not at all, P'Freeze.

00:47:46.080 --> 00:47:47.360
You are a good man.

00:47:49.240 --> 00:47:50.600
You're decent.

00:47:52.120 --> 00:47:54.560
The best man I've ever met.

00:47:57.920 --> 00:47:58.920
But...

00:48:00.640 --> 00:48:03.440
I can't keep forcing myself anymore.

00:48:06.600 --> 00:48:08.120
I'm so sorry.

00:48:11.520 --> 00:48:13.520
I'm really sorry.

00:48:30.360 --> 00:48:33.240
I'm just so afraid of hurting
a good person like you.

00:48:36.760 --> 00:48:37.760
It's okay.

00:48:39.720 --> 00:48:40.720
I understand.

00:49:19.680 --> 00:49:21.520
Can you look after the café for a bit?

00:49:21.760 --> 00:49:23.560
- Of course.
- I'm not feeling very well.

00:49:23.760 --> 00:49:26.120
I'm going to lie down for a moment.

00:49:26.240 --> 00:49:28.000
No problem, P'Toh. Go get some rest.

00:49:29.040 --> 00:49:31.480
Oh, and if P'Freeze shows up,

00:49:32.360 --> 00:49:33.360
please come get me.

00:49:33.400 --> 00:49:34.600
Will do.

00:49:58.800 --> 00:50:01.040
Welcome. What can I get for you?

00:50:02.000 --> 00:50:04.679
A hot Americano to go, please.

00:50:04.680 --> 00:50:05.760
Coming right up.

00:50:55.760 --> 00:50:57.296
(Next Episode)
P'Toh broke up with Dr. Freeze?

00:50:57.320 --> 00:50:59.960
It was P'Toh who ended it himself.

00:51:00.760 --> 00:51:02.600
Do you think he'll go back to Jimmy?

00:51:02.880 --> 00:51:05.080
Why would I go back to
someone who never truly loved me?

00:51:05.640 --> 00:51:06.760
From now on,

00:51:07.360 --> 00:51:08.720
I'm only going to love myself.

00:51:09.480 --> 00:51:12.360
Jim isn't doing any better
than P'Toh right now.

00:51:12.520 --> 00:51:16.880
Since he heard that P'Toh might move to England
with the doctor, he's completely shut himself in.

00:51:17.200 --> 00:51:19.520
I'm scared he might do something reckless.